nodes.bodyText:
Just 2 notes before starting to review this:


Wouldn't be better/simpler just to add an abstract method to CliCommand? like abstract CompletionStage<RestResponse> invokeInServer(RestClient client, Resource resource);


Also, I would remove the execute overload and use Resource as parameter since there is no difference between execute implementations.

